Free Flow Speed Outliers¶

Here we see there are a few Free Flow Spd (mph) values much lower than the others
These are the most easterly segments of West Main, as traffic slows into the Michikal/Stadium intersection

Free Flow Speed (mph) Standard Dev: 3.8 - Mean: 43.243 - Min: 21.8 - Max: 47.42

Removing Free Flow outliers beyond 2X std dev
Min is now 38.6 vs 21.8
This will yield a better visualization for Free Flow Speed
